    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introdução a PyGObject Module</title>

      <para>
        PyGObject-&pygobject2-version; provides <application>Python 2</application>
bindings to the GObject class from <application>GLib</application>.
      </para>

      &lfs113_checked;

